Enum Constant Detail

Pending

public static final ApprovalItem.ProvisioningState Pending
The plan has been executed, but the changes have not been completed. This is the default state the UI maps to null.

Finished

public static final ApprovalItem.ProvisioningState Finished
The plan has been executed and the changes have been applied and verified.

Unverifiable

public static final ApprovalItem.ProvisioningState Unverifiable
The plan has been executed but this item was not found in the application's schema and therefore can not be verified by the scanner.

Commited

public static final ApprovalItem.ProvisioningState Commited
The plan has been executed and successfully applied by an integration. The object has yet to be verify, which will take it to the Finished state.

Failed

public static final ApprovalItem.ProvisioningState Failed
The plan has been executed and there was a failure indicated by the integration.

Retry

public static final ApprovalItem.ProvisioningState Retry
The plan has been executed but had a non fatal error that will be retried.
